.SH "EXAMPLES"
.sp
Introduction
.sp
.B Example 1. Basic Color Image
.br
.RS 4
.sp
\f(CRrtwizard m35.g component\fP
.sp
Results in a default color image of the m35 truck, output to
rtwizard.pix
.RE
.sp
.B Example 2. Line Drawing Image
.br
.RS 4
.sp
\f(CRrtwizard \-d /dev/ogl m35.g \-l component\fP
.sp
Results in a line drawing of the m35 truck being display in an OpenGL
framebuffer
.RE
.sp
.B Example 3. Complex Image
.br
.RS 4
.sp
\f(CRrtwizard \-d /dev/ogl \-i m35.g \-c component/power.train \-g component \-l component\fP
.sp
Results in a view of the m35 truck highlighting the engine (in color)
with the truck being shown as a ghosted, edged background.
.RE
.sp
.B Example 4. Complex Image with Non\-Default View
.br
.RS 4
.sp
\f(CRrtwizard \-d /dev/ogl \-i m35.g \-c component/power.train \-g component \-l component \-a \-35 \-e 15 \-z 1.6\fP
.sp
Same as the previous image, except viewing the truck from a different
direction and zoomed in closer.
.RE
.sp
.B Example 5. Multiple Color Objects
.br
.RS 4
.sp
\f(CRrtwizard \-d /dev/ogl \-i m35.g \-c component/power.train,component/suspension \-z 1.6\fP
.sp
View the power train and suspension of the truck as color objects.
.RE
